---
title: Curry Beef Noodles with Coconut and Crispy Shallots
description: Khao Soi meets chow mein and slow-roasted pulled beef for a Thai-inspired dinner that's ready in 20 min! Creamy coconut broth, bright lime, fresh cilantro and crispy shallots top this delicious noodle dish!
